      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this dependable ride that's ready for its next chapter! While it shows some honest signs of use and age, it remains a solid and functional vehicle that gets the job done. It\u2019s a great opportunity for someone looking for a reliable driver at a more accessible price point. Come see the potential in this well-loved car!",
