    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but the suspension is beginning to feel loose and it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid choice for someone looking for an affordable entry-point vehicle who doesn't mind investing a bit of work into cosmetic and minor mechanical upkeep.",
