    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the exterior shows some noticeable scratches and minor dings consistent with its age. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and tear, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain functional. It is a solid, functional car for someone looking for dependable transportation without the premium price of a showroom-quality model.",
