    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic refinement. This model has been meticulously maintained to ensure consistent performance and long-term driver satisfaction. Featuring a suite of premium amenities and a documented service history, it offers a sophisticated driving experience for the discerning professional. We invite you to inspect this exceptional offering, which represents a premier balance of luxury and enduring value.",
      "price": 36800.0,
